### 折线图：华东区近7个月销售趋势
POST http://localhost:8087/test/tool/line-chart
Content-Type: application/json

{"months": 7, "regionName": "华东区", "title": "华东区近7个月销售趋势"}

### 柱状图：各大区销售额对比（宽范围覆盖全部测试数据）
POST http://localhost:8087/test/tool/bar-chart
Content-Type: application/json

{"dimension": "region", "startDate": "2025-01-01", "endDate": "2027-12-31", "title": "各大区销售额对比"}

